net.enilink.komma.core

Interface IStatement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IStatementPattern, Iterable<IStatement>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LinkedHashGraph.GraphStatement, Statement

    public interface IStatement
extends IStatementPattern, Iterable<IStatement>
    An RDF statement. A statement is equal to another statement if the subjects, predicates and objects are equal.

    The Iterable interface is implemented to simplify interactions with methods that require multiple statements.
